{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5e6b85e2-8970-42d0-8cae-0447bc8d9a07","content":"Here's what you need for your pod spec:\n\n**Environment variables** (on the container):\n\n```yaml\nenv:\n  # Enable automatic crash dumps\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n    value: \"1\"\n  # Dump type: 1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n    value: \"4\"\n  # Path to the createdump binary (required for NativeAOT)\n  - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpPath\n    value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n  # Where to write dumps (%d = PID, %t = timestamp)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n    value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%d.%t\"\n  # Optional: diagnostics if createdump itself fails\n  - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics\n    value: \"1\"\n```\n\n**Volume for dump storage** — use an `emptyDir` (or a PVC if you need persistence across pod restarts):\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: my-app\n      # ... your existing container spec ...\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: crash-dumps\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add: [\"SYS_PTRACE\"]   # createdump needs ptrace access\n  volumes:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi          # adjust based on expected dump size\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** is required — `createdump` uses `ptrace` to snapshot the process memory.\n- **`DOTNET_CreateDumpPath`** tells the NativeAOT runtime where to find `createdump` since it's not bundled with the app.\n- Use **dump type `2` (Heap)** instead of `4` (Full) if dump sizes are a concern.\n- If using an `emptyDir`, dumps are lost on pod eviction. Switch to a **PersistentVolumeClaim** if you need to retrieve dumps after crashes.\n- Ensure your container's `/proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern` isn't overridden by the node — `createdump` bypasses it, but verify in your cluster.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d6077fd5-6b89-47d2-aff0-b658a878db4e","outputTokens":587,"requestId":"6094:14BF27:2DB9C0:3B9A69:69FFE442"},"id":"339ad3fb-9d53-4842-b1f7-03955f7fb5a8","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:50:08.240Z","parentId":"24acb124-c79e-4b95-8f5e-76de6649521f"}
